summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of the north 250 feet of the south half of the northeast quarter of the northeast quarter of Section 11, Township 23 North, Range 4 East, W. M., with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto two new sections numbered 2-187 and 17-136, respectively.
